title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Feb 11 2022

description:
Biden's the last Dem left preaching "follow the science." Las Vegas kids cheer in the classroom when hearing they don’t have to wear masks. Dr. Marty Makary joins Clay and Buck to discuss the Johns Hopkins study on the ineffectiveness of lockdowns that was buried by the media, the truth about natural immunity, and public outrage at all the lies from the medical experts. Will Hillary be the Democrat nominee in 2024? Next GOP president should give Dr. Makary the Medal of Freedom. Caller suggests school boards are dropping mask mandates out of fear of being sued.
